Natalie Portman, 41, looked sensational at the Los Angeles premiere of Thor: Love And Thunder on Thursday evening. The Oscar winner dazzled in a tiny, gold, sequin mini dress which fell just above her thighs.The off-the-shoulder ensemble featured a glamorous cut-out across Natalie’s chest, which she drew attention to by wearing her brunette hair in a sleek bun.Natalie accessorised the look with some metallic strappy heels and bold makeup consisting of dramatic eyeshadow and bronze lipstick.Natalie takes the lead in Marvel’s latest instalment as superhero Thor.Speaking this week, Natalie revealed she worked with a trainer to get “as big as possible” to play the muscular character, according to Variety.